title: Dolphins News and Stuff That Brings Us Joy
itunes:title: Dolphins News and Stuff That Brings Us Joy
description:
A room filled with some heroes – Gregg Rosenthal, Marc Sessler, Henry Hodgson and Patrick Claybon bring you all of the latest news in the NFL including Tyreek Hill and Terron Armstead to the Dolphins, Panthers and Baker Mayfield having a “mutual disinterest,” and Malcolm Butler returning to the Patriots. We debut a PG segment called “Stuff That Brings Us Joy.”

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
